{
  "stem": "7556.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His wife was taking care of the sick ones and watching they shouldn't right away eat too much food, because this meant death.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had every morning an appel, they're called.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Jewish policemen were counting whether everybody is present that was supposed to be, and in the evening the same thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think Goldberg is anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think so, or maybe he is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know that his brother is-- his younger brother that I used to meet in the Krakow society meetings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were talking about that, the [INAUDIBLE], the one that saved me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't think he's alive, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Emalia at the very end, when they were taking us really to Plaszow, so they had a list.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the idea was to keep families together, let's say, my brother and myself, an elderly woman with her children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the-- the basis who is staying and who isn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then single people also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember when we were standing at the end of that selection, that a friend of ours was calling to Schindler, Herr Director, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was a very cute little girl, very cute, really, that had no relatives there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was not on the list, so Schindler came and grab her and put her on the good side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They went to-- to Auschwitz already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There would be many moments.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Among others, when that Australian pilot was shot down, and we all went to see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I will never forget the sight of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the name here, and the country Australia pinned to his--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he fell, he was already shot by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the ground, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
